thread.title: Alexander Toropov

author: Alexander Toropov
title: Alexander Toropov
text: I bought 3 packs from F9 Audio: Redwood Piano, House Nation and Electric Disco. There are just amazing. A full range of disco, nu disco, funk and of course classic house sound. Redwood is strong modern piano. I think it is good choice to start make music. Respect to Loopmasters and James Whiltshire. I love freemasons and will love it forewer. Their Shakedowns always in my playlist.
